    <text type="letter">
        <body>
            <pb xml:id="leaf001r" facs="loc_sd.00103.jpg" type="recto"/>

            <opener>
                <dateline>
                    <name type="place">Insane Asylum</name>
                    <name type="place">London Ontario</name>
                    <name type="place">London,</name>
                    <date when="1890-12-03">3 Dec 1890<ptr target="loc.07131_n1"/></date>
                </dateline>
            </opener>

            <p>Just a line, dear Walt, to say that Horace<ptr target="n4267"/> gives me a very good
                account of your condition&#8212;says you look and seem better and are a little more
                cheerful&#8212;all this is good and mighty pleasant to hear.</p>

            <p>In London, Ont. we have winter, snowed last night and sleighing today. All well and
                quiet, am going to town in a few minutes in my <hi rend="underline">cutter</hi>
                first time of using it this season</p>

            <closer><salute>Love to you</salute><signed>RM Bucke</signed></closer>

            <pb xml:id="leaf001v" facs="loc_sd.00104.jpg" type="verso"/>

        </body>
